                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>How Are Coins Made?</Header>
                <Paragraph>An animated overview of the six-step coin manufacturing process—blanking, annealing, upsetting, striking, inspecting, and counting and bagging—is available on the "Coins" web page..</Paragraph>
